  <div class="kicker">Account PPC Audit · Data pulled April 2026</div>
  <h1>What's actually happening in the account.</h1>
  <p class="lead">An honest read of the PPC work currently being done on the majority of the account. What's working, what's leaking money, what's missing entirely. Numbers drawn from Amazon Advertising reports and the Seller Central Business Report — each number labeled with its native reporting window.</p>

  <div class="legend">
