    <div class="legend-item"><span class="window-tag w64">64d</span> Search Term Report (19 Feb – 23 Apr)</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="window-tag w60">60d</span> Business Report revenue</div>
  </div>

  <div class="scope-banner">
    <strong>Scope:</strong> This audit covers 91.7% of the account — 7,428 active ASINs, 51 SP campaigns. A small portion of the catalog (5 parent products) is under separate management and has been excluded from every metric below.
  </div>

  <div class="hero-stats">
