  <div class="card gold">
    <h4>The headline</h4>
    <p>This part of the account runs lean on paper: 7.87x ROAS over 30 days, €1.14M in 60-day revenue. The numbers look healthy because the catalog is huge and a handful of auto-style mega-campaigns carry most of the weight. Underneath: 51 campaigns covering 7,428 ASINs, four of them with 12 ad groups each mixing hundreds of products, <strong>Top of Search converting at 16.64x ROAS but receiving only 0.8% of impressions</strong>, Sponsored Display essentially absent at €970 over 30 days, and €10K of identifiable waste sitting in the search-term report. The account isn't bleeding dramatically — it's under-managed.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="div">

