  <h2>The 5,388 invisible ASINs <span class="window-tag w60">60d</span></h2>

  <div class="card rose">
    <h4>The math</h4>
    <p>7,428 in-scope ASINs are live. 2,040 have at least one unit sold in the 60-day Business Report. <strong>5,388 ASINs — 72.5% of the active catalog — produced zero revenue in two months.</strong> Some are seasonal or discontinued, but a meaningful portion are simply ranked too deep in search results to be found.</p>
