      <li><strong>Realistic 90–120 day upside: +€63K monthly PPC sales</strong> through negation, TOS optimization, mega-campaign restructure, formal PAT, SD layer, and ranking campaigns on invisible ASINs. Most of the lift comes from work the account's own data already proves works.</li>
